info.name: restful-booker Api test
info.description:
Testing Restful-booker API for API Testing Project.

This the json body for api calls

``` json
{
    "firstname" : "name",
    "lastname" : "name",
    "totalprice" : "price",
    "depositpaid" : "price",
    "bookingdates" : {
        "checkin" : "Date",
        "checkout" : "Date"
    },
    "additionalneeds" : "meals"
}

 ```

Sample:

``` json
{
    "firstname" : "Sai",
    "lastname" : "kumar",
    "totalprice" : 1110,
    "depositpaid" : true,
    "bookingdates" : {
        "checkin" : "2025-05-27",
        "checkout" : "2025-06-18"
    },
    "additionalneeds" : "Lunch, Dinner"
}

 ```
